title: The Band - Blind Willie McTell / Remedy (1994 Live Promo CD Sing
description:
The Band - Blind Willie McTell / Remedy
Live Promo Cd - 1994 - Pyramid Records/Rhino Records


1. Blind Willie McTell (Bob Dylan) (live)
2. Remedy  (Colin Linden/Jim Weider) (live)

Promotional CD single, with live versions of two cuts from The Band&#039;s 1993 album Jericho. The credits say "supplied by Friday Night Videos, NBC". Presumably  sourced from The Band&#039;s appearance on the show (Friday Night Videos was a music video show broadcast on the American NBC television network from July 29, 1983 to May 24, 2002).

CDR / AIFF > FLAC level 8 in xACT1.58
